| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2249 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b960fde9-2183-5a04-bb81-0c1f8fe2f433"
